                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1369-18360509 t18360509-1369-punishment-200"></join>Confined Four Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury before Mr. Recorder</hi>.</p>
